The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | International | Thaksin arrest
                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Thaksin arrest
                            
	Bangkok, May 25 (Reuters): A Thai court issued orders today to arrest former Prime Minister Thaksin Shinawatra on terrorism charges in connection with riots over the past two months. Armed with the warrant, Thai prosecutors and the foreign ministry will launch a global hunt for the fugitive telecom tycoon.                                                                                                                                                           
